  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44480</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_036_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それにしても、さっきはびっくりしたね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That was really close...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44572</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_036_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まさか、あのダオスが出てくるなんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't believe it...was it really Dhaos the one that appeared in front of us?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_036_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだってんだよ、まったく。
オレら襲ってどうすんだって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the hell crawled up his ass, geez! Why was he trying to attack us!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_036_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだんだ！　突然現われて、突然襲ってくるなんて、
穏やかじゃねぇだーよ。ただの、卑怯もんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mmm... Appearing out of nowhere. Attacking out of nowhere. That's not very gentle at all. That's cowardice.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44980</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_036_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もし、大怪我でもしたら、おら絶対に許さなかったど！
金髪チャラチャラ、クールにすかしよってからに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If he catches me angry, he'll feel sorry about it! Just who the hell does that blonde jerk he is, acting all cool like that!? I'll mess him up!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45104</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_036_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだよ、珍しくオレらの心配してくれてんのか。
たまにはいいとこあんな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, now THIS is weird. You are worrying about me! I guess you aren't as bad as I thought!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_036_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何言ってるだ？　おらが心配なのは&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;だけだど。
チビ助やエト助がどうなろうと、おらの知ったことか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you going on about? I'm worried about my cute little &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;! You pest and Eto can fight alone for all I care.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_036_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何期待してたの……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Were you expecting a different answer?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45460</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_036_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>別にあんなヤツなんかに期待してねー……
期待なんてしてねーからな……っ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wasn't expecting crap from this closet! WHAT could I be expecting from YOU!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
